litiche.\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Lavorare in squadra per promuovere la collaborazione e l'efficienza del gruppo.\n6\ufe0f\u20e3 Preparati a svolgere con successo un colloquio di lavoro.", "short_description": "Potenzia le tue \"Soft Skills\" con il nostro simulatore di realt\u00e0 virtuale! Ideale per i professionisti che desiderano migliorare le proprie competenze interpersonali in modo immersivo e interattivo."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "SoftSkills_Logo_8100x1296px.png", "id": "1158856758691457", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974786_1158856762024790_8351105602424236604_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=uWah6QS11BgQ7kNvgFeMqdZ&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBYiLMfhYhIQDDQRzYfQpBRYboBcVBT3DQ3ypQXtCGrTg&oe=671F7869"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-portrait_1008x1440px.png", "id": "1001238441075007", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031591_1001238447741673_2783185145492224256_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=lXc003YMIsoQ7kNvgG6V_tA&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBuhGX3aH5AaNBFAkyiR9gH2fSOGAwwNH9M2XOR9x7VEw&oe=671F912F"}, {"file_name": "INVELON_Icon-512x512px.png", "id": "837105901661785", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476759_837105904995118_1711704673161247418_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Tjyg90qfdM0Q7kNvgEC_bd7&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD45UWjGhj4ggHXpk2Wd6lU3NaeF0OLDP4hb1Ztbu5D7A&oe=671F8673"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Hero-cover_3000x900px.png", "id": "436545955954692", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974777_436545959288025_6494250809818469750_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=HajIwVKKjMMQ7kNvgGQv9Aw&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCfoJpHYb